To open the web browser Firefox, according to the given desktop image where the 'Firefox W...' icon is visible, the actions are to move the cursor to the position of the Firefox icon and then double-click on it. the action sequence in JSON format would be:

```json
[
    {"action_type":"MouseAction","mouse_action_type":"double_click","mouse_button":"left","mouse_position":{"width":64,"height":43}}
]
```
